OL,3,CInquest into teen's death hears some
OL,4,Crailings were 'more permeable'
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a teenage
OL,7,Fgirl, who was swept into the sea at
OL,8,FWhitley Bay, has heard that some
OL,9,Frailings preventing access to the
OL,10,Flocation were "more permeable."
OL,12,FThirteen year old Edie Smart died last
OL,13,FJuly, four days after being rescued
OL,14,Ffrom the water.
OL,16,FShe'd been sat with a friend on
OL,17,Fdisused steps overlooking the beach
OL,18,Fwhen a surge of water pulled her in.
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@_O]
