FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780563951
OL,3,CInquest into teen's death hears some
OL,4,Crailings were 'more permeable'
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that access to those
OL,7,Fsteps, which had not been in use for
OL,8,Fmore than a decade, are prohibited by
OL,9,Ftwo sets of barriers, one of which was
OL,10,Freplaced in 2020 as part of work to
OL,11,Fthe seafront.
OL,13,F"Would you agree," said the coroner,
OL,14,F"they don't prevent access in the same
OL,15,Fway as the old railings? There are
OL,16,Fgaps in there and they are easy to
OL,17,Fbreach?"
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@RO]vD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
