FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780563951
OL,3,CInquest into teen's death hears some
OL,4,Crailings were 'more permeable'
OL,6,FJohn Sparkes, Director of Regeneration
OL,7,Fat North Tyneside Council, referred to
OL,8,Fthe railings in question as "more
OL,9,Fpermeable."
OL,11,F"Would it be fair to say," the coroner
OL,12,Fasked, "that those railings would be
OL,13,Fmore easily breached by someone
OL,14,Fsmaller, a child rather than an adult?"
OL,16,F"Yes," he replied.
OL,18,FMr Sparkes, however, had earlier
OL,19,Fdescribed it as "appropriate railing
OL,20,Ffor that location... used in multiple
OL,21,Flocations along our coastline."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@gO]
