FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780563951
OL,3,CInquest into teen's death hears some
OL,4,Crailings were 'more permeable'
OL,6,FThe coroner also inquired about a lack
OL,7,Fof warning signs.
OL,9,FMr Sparkes replied that expert
OL,10,Fguidance, generally, was "not to sign
OL,11,Fwhere there was a foreseeable risk."
OL,13,FThough he replied that the observation
OL,14,Fsuch risk may not be "inherently
OL,15,Fobvious to a child" was "fair."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
