PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780563951
OL,3,CInquest into teen's death hears some
OL,4,Crailings were 'more permeable'
OL,6,FDirector of Environment for North
OL,7,FTyneside Council Samantha Dand said
OL,8,Fthat its health and safety team
OL,9,Fchecked the location after the
OL,10,Fincident and no recommendations arose
OL,11,Ffrom that inspection.
OL,13,FThe inquest continues.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
